      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SLICK IVAN (2) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (22.57) at Geelong. Has a good winning strike rate at this journey. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Has ability and looks hard to stop. MAN OF COURAGE (1) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a scorching early split and ran away with a 0.7 lengths win at Warrnambool over 390m in 22.14. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. BEAR THE BRUNT (5) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.3 lengths at Warragul in a handy 22.46 beating Play Lab. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Leading chance again. ELECTROJET (7) generally performs well over this distance.",
